NOTE: js/gameState.test.js is provided for reference and validation.
To run tests, ensure Jest or similar test framework is configured:

  npm install --save-dev jest
  npx jest js/gameState.test.js

Alternatively, if you have a test setup already configured, simply run:
  npm test

The test suite validates all acceptance criteria:
1. gameState object tracks currentRound (1-10) and phase transitions
2. initializeGame() resets state to round 1, setup phase
3. advanceRound() increments round and handles game completion at round 10 (only after playing round 10)
4. Phase management functions work correctly
